--Submitter: David Chang (DavidChang@ami.com.tw) Fri, 14 May 2010 17:58:34 CST

Package: helper (1.0.4); urgency = critical

Abstract:
	Interrupt calls into helper driver were sleeping in mutex lock. Changed the locks to a combination of mutex and spinlocks to avoid sleeping within interrupt handler and to allow sleeping during other function calls. With these locks the list access is secured.

